Package cz.zcu.kiv.crce.example.indexer.internal

Class ImportIndexer

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.zcu.kiv.crce.plugin.AbstractPlugin
      • cz.zcu.kiv.crce.metadata.indexer.AbstractResourceIndexer
        • cz.zcu.kiv.crce.example.indexer.internal.ImportIndexer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ResourceIndexer, Plugin, Comparable<Plugin>, org.osgi.service.cm.ManagedService
    public class ImportIndexer
extends AbstractResourceIndexer
    This class represents example indexer (which is plugin in CRCE). This indexer (/plugin) will save JAR in temp folder in current system, extracts given JAR and then reads imported packages from all .class files in given JAR. Number of imported packages is saved as property of given resource and list of these packages is saved as requirement of this resource.
    Author:
    vit.mazin@seznam.cz
